## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Since this is a Vite/React application, I will run `npm run build` after making the changes to ensure that TypeScript compilation and Vite bundling succeed without any errors.

### Manual Verification
- The development server is currently running. We will manually inspect the changes in the browser (by opening the local URL) to confirm that the text, layout, and animations are functioning correctly with the new content.
